          .row
            .twelve.columns.split-40-60

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-1-1.chat-left
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat It’s tough isn’t it!!!
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-1-2.chat-right.raised
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat Yes it is. The ever lurching to the right of British politics and growing disparities in wealth and inequality with some of the most vulnerable people in our society being left behind and forgotten. Yes! It is tough!

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-1-3.chat-left
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat Nah not that!! Who cares about that!!
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-1-4.chat-right.raised
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat Oh ok!

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-1-5.chat-left
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat We mean, content...making stuff...all of the time! It’s a ball ache right! And expensive?
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-1-6.chat-right.raised
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat Yep! We’re not just brands anymore, we’re broadcasters and entertainers. And to do that we need to be creating stuff! Consistently creating stuff! If not, then we’re no longer relevant!
