  .sub-section
    .outer.outer-long
      .middle
        .inner

          .row
            .twelve.columns.split-60-40

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-2-1.chat-left-2
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat Exactly! And unless you have a budget the size of a Russian oligarch’s ‘pension fund’, what can you do?
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-2-2.chat-right-2.raised
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat Nothing!! We can do nothing but accept our inevitable and impending doom!!

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-2-3.chat-left-2
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat Well one thing you can do! Is to create short form content.
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-2-4.chat-right-2.raised
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat  But isn’t that a bit rubbish? It’s like proper content but not as good? Shorter in fact?

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-2-5.chat-left-2
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat It’s actually insanely effective when done well. Can be amazingly cost effective. Allows you to be more reactive and it also can be some of the most creative content executions you’ll get to produce.
                .highlight.highlight-pink.triangle-border.right.chat-2-6.chat-right-2
                  %p.brand.brand-pixel Brand:
                  %p.chat  Well smoke me a kipper, I'll be back for breakfast!!!

              .chat-block
                .highlight.highlight-blue.triangle-border.left.chat-2-7.chat-left-2
                  %p.brand.tanjun-blue Tanjun:
                  %p.chat Exactly! We think you should make a shed load! And if you want. We can make some for you! Here’s some of the short form stuff we’ve made. Take a look!


